Class Presenter

  • java.lang.Object
    • controller.Presenter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Observer

    public class Presenter
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Observer
    Author:
    Zeev Manilovich., Lital Gilboa. The Presenter class acts upon the model and the view. It retrieves data from repositories (the model), and formats it for display in the view. Presenter implements Observer in order to observe changes in View and Model Interfaces.
